TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT S_DACOM_MTET_Config.mterm_type, S_DACOM_MTET_Config.PtyLocNum, S_DACOM_Device.device_id, S_DACOM_Device.description, S_DACOM_Device.serial_no, S_DACOM_Device.manufacturer, S_DACOM_Device.model_group, UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B.c_long, UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_long, S_DACOM_Class_Code.c_long FROM S_DACOM_MTET_Config, S_DACOM_Device, UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M, UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B, S_DACOM_Class_Code WHERE S_DACOM_MTET_CONFIG.mterm_stat ='N' and S_DACOM_Device.device_type ='MTET' and S_DACOM_Class_Code.c_code='X' and S_DACOM_MTET_Config.Device_ID=S_DACOM_Device.Device_ID and S_DACOM_Device.Manufacturer*=UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_short and s_dacom_device.Model_Group*=UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B.c_short and S_DACOM_MTET_CONFIG.mterm_type*=S_DACOM_Class_Code.c_short and S_DACOM_MTET_CONFIG.PtyLocNum=$$Property_no and S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum=$$Property_no and UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B.PtyLocNum=$$Property_no and UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.PtyLocNum=$$Property_no and S_DACOM_Class_Code.PtyLocNum=$$Property_no
